<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B0A3275FF9F80ECFDAC285EFD42" author="Di-Nizo, C. B. &amp; Ventura, K. &amp; Ferguson-Smith, M. A. &amp; O'Brien, P. C. M. &amp; Yonenaga-Yassuda, Y. &amp; Silva, M. J. J." box="[914,1141,618,645]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75" pagination="0117579" refId="ref66405" refString="Di-Nizo, C. B., Ventura, K., Ferguson-Smith, M. A., O'Brien, P. C. M., Yonenaga-Yassuda, Y. &amp; Silva, M. J. J. (2015) Comparative chromosome painting in six species of Oligoryzomys (Rodentia, Sigmodontinae) and the karyotype evolution of the genus. Public Library of Science one, 10 (2), e 0117579. https: // doi. org / 10.1371 / journal. pone. 0117579" type="journal article" year="2015">
